           \n                <img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=1000w\" width=\"600\" height=\"1018\" srcset=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/51e8148de4b01c1eb79c1977/f2333a8e-b7d4-4719-a0ee-043a08e51bac/emperor_card_process-ezgif.com-cut+%281%29.gif?format=2500w 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\n            \n          \n        \n          \n        \n\n        \n      \n        </figure>\n      \n\n    \n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  <p><br />I’m already looking forward to drawing the next card, and deepening/expanding my skills and process for this kind of archetypal illustration. probably if I draw the Emperor again in 3 years, it’ll look very different. </p><p>next, I’m thinking: The Empress?  </p><p>🔹</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n<hr />\n\n\n  <p><a href=\"https://